description:
Roberto Torres is an comic artist/inker/colorist living in the Orlando area. His coloring work has been in titles by IDW and several indy companies. (Creature Entertainment, CAE, Hashtag Comics). His pencils have been published by Creature Entertainment. He currently has pencils and inks for Resistance Entertainment's Blackbird Issue 2, along with being the Penciler/Inker/Colorist and co-creator for Souls Eternal from Hashtag Comics and the colorist for Tailwands from Hashtag Comics.

He is married and recently celebrated his 8th anniversary to his wife. He has one toy poodle.
name: Roberto Torres
